    "media:imagetext": "PA4\nSleeperette* service is offered on First-Class flights\nat no extra charge ... Berths are $55 extra.\nEurope is only a dream away\n—when Uncle Sam's your Skipper\nYou sense the difference when you step aboard\na big Pan Am Clipper*—to head for Europe\nwith the only U. S. airline that specializes in\noverseas travel.\nSome say it's the friendliness of Pan Am's\npeople. Others credit the roomy, long-range\nplanes. And all agree that when you know Pan\nAmerican meets Uncle Sam's strictest rules of\nairline operation with a generous margin to spare,\nit adds up to an assurance which makes the\nhours fly by.\nAs so many experienced travelers have said:\n\"Pan Am knows how to run an airline.\" For\nreservations, call your Travel Agent or Pan Am.\nMore people fly to Europe by\nPAN AMERICAN\nWORLD'S MOST EXPERIENCED AIRLINE",
